3. Project Naming Guidance
Projects should be outcomes, not just categories: Good project names:
"Install New Blinds"
"Maryland Energy Grant Application"
"Plan Summer Vacation"
"Fix Basement Water Issue"
Bad project names:
"Home Improvement" (too broad)
"To Do" (not an outcome)
"Meg" (not a project)
